Company Description: Established IN 1948, Mcdonald's Is One Of The Leading Global Foodservice Retailers IN The World. Its Menu Consists Of Various Items, Including Burgers, Sandwiches, Chicken, Breakfast, Salads, Snacks And Sides, Beverages, Desserts And Shakes. The Firm Operates More Than 32,000 Local Restaurants Serving Over 60 Million People IN 117 Countries Each Day. For Over 20 Years, Mcdonald's Has Maintained Its Partnership With Environmental Defense Fund, A Nonprofit Organization Specializing IN Creating Transformational Solutions For Environmental Problems.

Founded IN 1955, Mcdonald S Is A Global Food Service Retailer That Operates More Than 30,000 Locations IN Over 100 Countries. The Restaurant Serves Various Shakes, Hamburgers, Grilled And Fried Chicken Products, Salads, Fruits, Sandwiches And Fish.
